{
  "texts": [
    "The findings underscore the need for ethical and responsible integration of ChatGPT, continuous monitoring of its impact, and addressing under-researched areas to maximize benefits and minimize risks in educational contexts.According to Marín-Guamán [26], the study on the advantages and disadvantages of ChatGPT highlights its high precision and continuous learning ability, as well as its versatility in a wide range of applications in higher education, despite certain limitations.",
    "ChatGPT ability to automate tasks makes it a valuable tool in the educational realm and other contexts.",
    "Based on a probabilistic sample in Ecuador and using an unsupervised learning approach, the study shows how ChatGPT can improve the quality and efficiency of online communication and virtual assistance applications.",
    "A key conclusion is that ChatGPT has the potential to be useful for both students and teachers in higher education, although it is crucial to recognize its limitations to address new topics critically and reflectively.",
    "The success of its integration in education will depend on its use and incorporation in teaching and learning processes."
  ]
}